{"tid":1444294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句：人多，Make Noise，全！部！轉！場！，當係我求下你地","createTime":"2019-08-11T12:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:07:14.000Z","uid":285814,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"83de9aeb42a21d9050b0ff5a4ed8006633168be0","tid":1444294,"uid":285814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:03:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我真係求下各位勇武 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家已經有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多過200個手足</span></span>比人拉左，6.12到依家差唔多兩個月，有幾多次真係有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">BE WATER</span></span> ?　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依一場係一場<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">漫長</span></span>嘅仗，依家亦<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係生死仗</span></span>嘅日子（eg, 6.12 立會二讀送中) <br />\n各位麻煩冷一冷靜，諗下點解依家要個個星期都出黎遊行<br />\n要<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">諗下咩行動先係最有用同最實際</span>！　<br />\n一直講要BE WATER, 唔好再無意義咁守 ! <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">人多，make noise ，之後</span><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全！部！轉！場！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">要避免不必要犧牲！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d7ded15ecdb77ac29b9e6a1d451ba82a4ea9cf","tid":1444294,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:03:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d481dcfaa69f3b36d9936f40657f4b983a02929","tid":1444294,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:04:40.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港警察</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">知法犯法</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">下流賤格</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一味靠嚇</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">污糟邋遢</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">淪為垃圾</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">吞槍自殺</span></div></strong></span></blockquote><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"383ab7348c5ee7c8a298059240ab0ba9f9292425","tid":1444294,"uid":285814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:05:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"accd3ac54ae5291f1b23c79323d991bfc6519a79","tid":1444294,"uid":285814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:06:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0fc1eed5a06f6ca63432ea1f74a2a03e238ba98","tid":1444294,"uid":285814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:06:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68d5c0f25428d96fa04705a46c34b1efc45ea7c6","tid":1444294,"uid":285814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:06:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06dd7d63ba739e73c07cdc1a5d7ab06e9effe0eb","tid":1444294,"uid":285814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:06:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74c7e2a5f15ab220fb868fca838230e4e20f2183","tid":1444294,"uid":285814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:07:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbdd834a8c0c1a12f4c75f09a3fb54d89d8fee4a","tid":1444294,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:07:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"}]}